Package edu.umb.cs682.ecom.backend.repositories

Interface TokenWhitelist

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CrudRepository<Token,​String>, MongoRepository<Token,​String>, PagingAndSortingRepository<Token,​String>, QueryByExampleExecutor<Token>, Repository<Token,​String>
    public interface TokenWhitelist
extends MongoRepository<Token,​String>
    TokenWhitelist manages access to the MongoDB related to Tokens. In particular, it manages the whitelist of tokenIDs, granting or restricting access to mappings which require authentication.
